{"tid":711964,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得做球皇基本要求係國家隊同球會都有好表現","createTime":"2018-06-21T21:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T06:08:07.000Z","uid":187161,"like":72,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f16ea7c8aa2b2340995e273634e3d94e70aab479","tid":711964,"uid":187161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:06:49.000Z","msg":"理性分析最少都應該有團火先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係話小花唔勁 勁係勁 但講真比你係球會踢到曉飛 一踢國家隊就失蹤頭dupdup憑咩又做隊長又做球皇 出大巴啦仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反 牙朗球會同國家隊都咁有火 好難唔覺得佢係球皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇番以前比人話球皇個啲 差唔多全部都係國家隊同球會都好好表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係講個人數據 跑動已經足以證明球員有無heart踢<br />\n<br />\n利申：兩個都欣賞 但睇完呢兩場真係對小花好失望"},{"pid":"64b61282da6672043885603416768553c57c7cf7","tid":711964,"uid":41093,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:10:50.000Z","msg":"上屆咪亞軍囉 算好啦"},{"pid":"a8f9bd47cd88e47b90ea62cd6e4d2962b8932528","tid":711964,"uid":187161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:12:39.000Z","msg":"淨係識散步 唔走位人地比唔到波你又拉唔到空位出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30d5fe504d2eaf0d1076b88e6fc9d8b91d378b7","tid":711964,"uid":187161,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"64b61282da6672043885603416768553c57c7cf7","tid":711964,"uid":41093,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:10:50.000Z","msg":"上屆咪亞軍囉 算好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:13:42.000Z","msg":"真係抵佢攞唔到冠軍"},{"pid":"f03d73ed9aa06b302f27ac37b6198f19a16aca26","tid":711964,"uid":165817,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:15:16.000Z","msg":"最起碼真係應該要有團火同領導能力<br />\n<br />\n幾時見過一個王係咁冇霸氣<br />\n除咗昏君"},{"pid":"ac9f37b997d7569